Harper Says He Expects Canada Economy to Continue Growing Slowly

-- B y   A n d r e w   M a y e d a
-- 
2011-09-20T17:19:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/harper-says-he-expects-canada-economy-to-continue-growing-slowly.html
Canadian Prime Minister  Stephen
Harper  said he expects the country’s economy to continue growing
“slowly.”  Harper, speaking to reporters in  New York , said he is
monitoring the global economic situation and is prepared to make
“appropriate” changes to his government’s fiscal plan if
needed.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Mayeda in Ottawa at 
 amayeda@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
